## How this project works

This project is organized as independent Databricks Asset Bundles — one per component. Each bundle can be developed, validated, and deployed on its own lifecycle.

| Bundle | What it does | Deploy order |
|--------|-------------|--------------|
{%- if include_retriever == "yes" %}
| [**retriever**](./retriever/README.md) | Data ingestion, preprocessing, and Vector Search index | 1st |
{%- endif %}
{%- if include_tools == "yes" %}
| [**tools**](./tools/README.md) | UC functions used by the agent | 2nd |
{%- endif %}
{%- if include_agent == "yes" %}
| [**agent**](./agent/README.md) | LangGraph agent, evaluation, model serving, and chat app | 3rd |
{%- endif %}
{%- if include_evaluation == "yes" %}
| [**evaluation**](./evaluation/README.md) | Golden-dataset curator app + trace merge job | any time |
{%- endif %}

Shared variables (`uc_catalog`, `schema`) are defined once in `global_bundle.yml` and included by every bundle.

