## Development workflow

```
edit agent_config.yml       ← add a retriever or tool
       ↓
make generate               ← regenerates resource YAML + code stubs
       ↓
implement TODOs             ← fill in tool/retriever logic
       ↓
make deploy TARGET=dev      ← validate + upload
       ↓
databricks bundle run ...   ← run the job
```

