## CI/CD

GitHub Actions workflows validate each bundle against `staging` and `prod` on every pull request that touches the corresponding directory.

| Workflow | Triggers on changes to |
|----------|----------------------|
{%- if include_retriever == "yes" %}
| `retriever-bundle-ci.yml` | `retriever/**` |
{%- endif %}
{%- if include_tools == "yes" %}
| `tools-bundle-ci.yml` | `tools/**` |
{%- endif %}
{%- if include_agent == "yes" %}
| `agent-bundle-ci.yml` | `agent/**` |
{%- endif %}
{%- if include_evaluation == "yes" %}
| `evaluation-bundle-ci.yml` | `evaluation/**` |
{%- endif %}

Required GitHub secrets:

| Secret | Used by |
|--------|---------|
| `STAGING_DATABRICKS_CLIENT_ID` | All bundles |
| `STAGING_DATABRICKS_CLIENT_SECRET` | All bundles |
| `PROD_DATABRICKS_CLIENT_ID` | All bundles |
| `PROD_DATABRICKS_CLIENT_SECRET` | All bundles |

